Open Source Software Conference (OSSC) OSOL is a one day event, the biggest main linux event at Hungary, celebrating after the world Software Freedom Day at Szeged's Science and IT University. Lots of talks (around 40), lots of participants, developers, hackers, business groups - lot of fun. See OSOL_Conference_Szeged_2012

VDay is a one day event in Hungary around virtualisation theme. Lot of attendees, companies, and serious talks, mostly in hungarian. See VDay_Hungary_2012.
LinuxDay is a small event in Austria near the Swiss, German, and Lichtenstein border. See LinuxDay Dornbirn 2012.
